rows.label: qst005802_msg0001
rows.name:
So this is the Isle of Sleeping Remains
of which those writings told...

rows.label: qst005802_msg0002
rows.name: Was there really a kingdom here?

rows.label: qst005802_msg0003
rows.name:
It's hard to believe when the place
looks so...empty.

rows.label: qst005802_msg0004
rows.name:
You think it was overrun by monsters
or something, and they just...y'know,
crushed everything?

rows.label: qst005802_msg0005
rows.name:
It is a possibility...
Let us dig!

rows.label: qst005802_msg0007
rows.name:
Though the buildings on the surface
may be destroyed, some traces would
surely be left beneath the ground.

rows.label: qst005802_msg0008
rows.name: Now, let us unearth those secrets!

rows.label: qst005802_msg0009
rows.name:
Kubira, I am afraid this may not be
a realistic plan. Apart from anything,
it would take far too much time.

rows.label: qst005802_msg0010
rows.name:
This is an order from your king.
Commence digging at once!

rows.label: qst005802_msg0011
rows.name: Kubira not listening even little bit...

rows.label: qst005802_msg0012
rows.name: Come on, guys. We've come this far.

rows.label: qst005802_msg0013
rows.name: Let's at least try to do as Kubira asks.

rows.label: qst005802_msg0014
rows.name:
Once you take on a job,
you see it through!

rows.label: qst005802_msg0015
rows.name:
Not another one of your
Salvager's Code thingies...

rows.label: qst005802_msg0016
rows.name:
But all right, let's see if we can
do this thing.
